Cadel:

CTRE’s Phoenix 5 API has been deprecated which forced my team to use the phoenix 6 API to control our Falcons

Deprecation doesn’t force you to do anything this year. It does mean that they say they’ll remove it next year, so you could keep using Phoenix 5 this year and change to Phoenix 6 next year.
